正垃圾

One of the WORST restaurants ever. Terrible food, terrible service, terrible everything.

went there for lunch and ordered charsiu & overeasy rice. tasty charsiu, large portion. the only bad thing is the charsiu seemed to be chopped carelessly into HUGE pieces!

the seating arrangement was comfortable, but actually not many tables available. so do reserve in advanced for busy hours.

Wonton, noodles and 炸両 👍🏻
Deep fried prawn 🍤 toast 
Was too oily and not crispy 
But overall was good 👍🏻😋😋
Rubbish owners. Rubbish food. Beware of food poisoning and brainwashed swine.
